text.tspan: App tracks activity, weight, food, hydration, and sleep.
Platform is intuitively designed and easy to navigate.
Gives user ability to set up competitive challenges with friends.
User earns badges and milestones for added motivation.
App is tied to one specific tracking device.
Tracking features tend to be very innacurate.
User in unable to edit their fitness stats.
Constant tracking & feedback can give user anxiety.
Target users who tried Fitbit and were unhappy with results.
App has a 4.3 rating in app store. We can aim higher.
The platform is loaded with features. We can simplify the scope.
Provide syncing ability with all fitness tracking devices.
User base is massive and very diverse.
Company has large budget and product support.
Users view the competition feature is addictive.
Fitbit brand recognition has gained momentum.
